<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Britannia </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Britannia is bordered to the west by Riverdale Park, traveling along the Elbow River; the park has pedestrian bridge access to River Park, Sandy Beach Park, and Altadore Park,
                providing easy access to outdoor activities from picnics to jogging to simply taking in the fresh air.
            </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Elbow Drive provides quick access to downtown and to 4th Street, known for its abundance
                of cafés, restaurants, and shops, making it one of the most popular destinations in Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">4th Street in intersected by Uptown 17th business revitalization zone, and is several
                kilometers of shops, restaurants, clubs, and bars, making it an entertainment center for all times of
                the day. Whether it’s the owner-run shops or the wild night out you prefer, there is bound to be
                something to catch your fancy.</p>

            <p class="par-lg">There are currently no schools in Britannia, but schools K-12 are available in close
                proximately in the surrounding area.</p>
        </div>
